name: Kyle RAINEY, Petitioner v. Seth WILLIAMS, Head of Philadelphia District Attorney's Office

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 19th day of June, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and “Emergency Motion” are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
